		'published' : '2012-01-04 23:35:55',
		'status' : 1,
		'summary' : '',
		'body' : '<a href=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/virt_meet01.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-2342\" title=\"virt_meet01\" src=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/virt_meet01-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Get three days of ICD-10 training without the travel. This <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-9989/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">online event, February 29-March 2, 2012</a>, will feature two tracks: One for HIM Directors and Coding Supervisors and another for Inpatient and Outpatient Coders.\r\n\r\nThis <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-9989/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">one-of-a-kind virtual summit</a> will offer practical, hands-on guidance for the challenges of ICD-10 preparation and implementation. You won\'t have to budget for travel or brave uncertain weather to hear presentations from faculty and dialogue with these experts as well as your peers.\r\n\r\nYou\'ll be able to access presentations, question and answer sessions, and networking opportunities from any computer or conference room without having to leave the office. This event offers attendees continuing education credits to maintain their credentials, access to JustCoding editors and your peers in networking forums, and a virtual exhibit hall.\r\n\r\nFollowing the live event, all attendees will have ongoing on-demand access to all of the Summit sessions and content. <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-9989/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">Click here to learn more about this upcoming Virtual Summit</a>, including the agenda, speakers, and pricing.',
