		'title' : 'JustCoding Virtual Summit now offers AHIMA credits',
		'published' : '2012-02-08 14:32:54',
		'status' : 1,
		'summary' : '',
		'body' : 'Did you know you can earn up to 12 AHIMA credits by attending the <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-10190/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">JustCoding Virtual Summit: ICD-10-CM and ICD-10-PCS</a> February 29-March2?\r\n\r\nThe summit features two tracks, one for HIM directors and coding supervisors and one for inpatient and outpatient coders. Each track offers six sessions, but participants have on demand access to all of the sessions for six months. That means you can earn a total of 12 AHIMA CEs and gain practical, hands-on guidance for the challenges of ICD-10 preparation and implementation.\r\n\r\nWe plan to have other credits available for the summit, so stay tuned for more credit information in the near future.\r\n\r\nThe summit is less than three weeks away, so sign up today!',
