		'body' : 'As promised, more news about continuing education credits for the <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-10190/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">JustCoding Virtual Summit: ICD-10-CM and ICD-10-PCS</a>. We are now offering up to 12 AAPC credits for attendees.\r\n\r\nThe summit features two tracks, one for HIM directors and coding supervisors and one for inpatient and outpatient coders. Each track offers six sessions, but participants have on demand access to all of the sessions for six months. That means you can earn a total of 12 AAPC CEs and gain practical, hands-on guidance for the challenges of ICD-10 preparation and implementation.\r\n\r\nAnd those are in addition to the 12 AHIMA credits we announced earlier. You can earn both AAPC and AHIMA for attending each session, it’s not an either/or deal. So you can rack up a total of 24 credits while getting ready for the switch to ICD-10.\r\n\r\nWhat are you waiting for? <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-10190/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">Sign up now</a>!',
