		'status' : 1,
		'summary' : '',
		'body' : 'In addition to AAPC and AHIMA continuing education credits, attendees to the <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-10190/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">JustCoding Virtual Summit: ICD-10-CM and ICD-10-PCS</a> can also earn up to 12 credits from the <a href=\"http://www.hcpro.com/acdis/\">Association of Clinical Documentation Specialists (ACDIS)</a>.\r\n\r\nClinical documentation improvement (CDI) specialists can pick up credits while learning about the new coding conventions and guidelines as well as how to obtain the appropriate level of documentation from physicians. CDI specialists can also pick up tips about how to work with physicians now to improve documentation before ICD-10-CM/PCS goes live.\r\n\r\nDon’t miss your chance to get a jump on improving documentation early to make the transition smoother. <a href=\"http://www.hcmarketplace.com/ev-10190/JustCoding-Virtual-Summit-ICD10CM-and-ICD10PCS.html\">Sign up today</a>!',
