		'title' : 'Where does your ICD-10 implementation stand? WEDI wants to know',
		'published' : '2013-02-11 15:31:19',
		'status' : 1,
		'summary' : '',
		'body' : 'The Workgroup for Electronic Data Interchange (WEDI) is conducting an <a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/WEDISurveyICD-10\">ICD-10 readiness survey</a> through February 20.\r\n\r\nWEDI and CMS will use the survey results to measure the:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Progress of ICD-10 implementation</li>\r\n	<li>Impact of the compliance date extension to October 1, 2014</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe survey is open to anyone associated with healthcare organizations, including vendors, health plans, and healthcare providers.',
		'meta_keywords' : '',
