		'publication' : 'justcoding-website',
		'resource_type' : NULL,
		'title' : 'CMS releases second ICD-10 NCD transmittal',
		'published' : '2013-03-28 11:43:39',
		'status' : 1,
		'summary' : '',
		'body' : 'CMS <a href=\"https://www.cms.gov/Regulations-and-Guidance/Guidance/Transmittals/Downloads/R1199OTN.pdf\"><em>Transmittal 1199</em></a> updates the national coverage determination (NCD) hard-coded shared system edits to include ICD-10-CM codes.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/news01.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-3371\" title=\"news01\" src=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/news01-300x193.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"193\" /></a>CMS included 30 spreadsheets with the transmittal. The spreadsheets indicate affected ICD-9 codes and their corresponding ICD-10 codes as they relate to their respective NCDs, in addition to the rest of the coding infrastructure specific to each NCD.\r\n\r\nEach spreadsheet contains the following information:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>NCD Number/Title</li>\r\n	<li>Internet-Only Manual (IOM) searchable link related to the NCD</li>\r\n	<li>Medicare Coverage Database (MCD) searchable link related to the NCD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCMS plans to translate approximately 40% of the roughly 330 current NCDs from ICD-9-CM to ICD-10-CM.\r\n\r\nTransmittal 1199 is the second of three “omnibus” transmittals with the NCD translations. CMS released the first, <em><a href=\"http://www.cms.gov/Regulations-and-Guidance/Guidance/Transmittals/downloads/R1122OTN.pdf\">Transmittal R1122OTN</a>, </em>September 14, 2012. The final release will be sometime later in 2013.\r\n\r\nYou can review the <a href=\"https://www.cms.gov/Regulations-and-Guidance/Guidance/Transmittals/Downloads/R1199OTN.pdf\">transmittal</a> and related <em><a href=\"http://www.cms.gov/Outreach-and-Education/Medicare-Learning-Network-MLN/MLNMattersArticles/Downloads/MM8197.pdf\">MLN Matters</a></em> article on the CMS website.',
		'meta_keywords' : '',
		'volume' : NULL,
		'issue' : NULL,
		'article_position' : NULL
