		'body' : 'HCPro wants to provide you with the most helpful educational tools and information to prepare you and your institution for ICD-10 implementation. Please take this quick survey to help us continue to target your needs.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/89P2PZJ\">Click here</a> to take this survey.',
