		'body' : 'Our sister publication<b>, Medical Records Briefing,</b> is conducting a benchmarking survey on ICD-10 implementation, and we would appreciate your input. Please take a few moments to complete this survey.\r\n\r\nSimply <a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/M8YTKSR\">click here</a> to answer the survey questions online. You should only need 5-10 minutes to answer the survey.\r\n\r\nThank you for input!',
