		'summary' : '',
		'body' : 'Which tasks have you completed on your ICD-10 implementation list? We want to know.<a href=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/question-marks.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-3439\" alt=\"question marks\" src=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/question-marks-300x300.jpg\" width=\"133\" height=\"133\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOur sister publication<b>, Medical Records Briefing,</b> is conducting a benchmarking survey on ICD-10 implementation, and we would appreciate your input. Please take a few moments to complete this survey.\r\n\r\nSimply <a href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/M8YTKSR\">click here</a> to answer the survey questions online. You should only need 5-10 minutes to answer the survey.\r\n\r\nYou know you have been bombarded with surveys about ICD-10, so we thank you for input!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;',
