		'body' : 'CMS is asking for some social media help in support of ICD-10. The agency is planning a <a href=\"http://links.govdelivery.com/track?type=click&amp;enid=ZWFzPTEmbWFpbGluZ2lkPTIwMTUwNDE0LjQ0MDgzNDgxJm1lc3NhZ2VpZD1NREItUFJELUJVTC0yMDE1MDQxNC40NDA4MzQ4MSZkYXRhYmFzZWlkPTEwMDEmc2VyaWFsPTE3NDM4MzU1JmVtYWlsaWQ9bWxlcHBlcnRAaGNwcm8uY29tJnVzZXJpZD1tbGVwcGVydEBoY3Byby5jb20mZmw9JmV4dHJhPU11bHRpdmFyaWF0ZUlkPSYmJg==&amp;&amp;&amp;101&amp;&amp;&amp;http://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Coding/ICD10/Latest_News.html\">social media rally</a> to encourage the healthcare community to get ready for the ICD-10 transition.<a href=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/dont-miss-it.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright  wp-image-3608\" src=\"http://blogs.hcpro.com/icd-10/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/dont-miss-it-300x252.jpg\" alt=\"dont miss it\" width=\"164\" height=\"138\" /></a>\r\n\r\nYou can sign up to take part in the <a href=\"http://links.govdelivery.com/track?type=click&amp;enid=ZWFzPTEmbWFpbGluZ2lkPTIwMTUwNDE0LjQ0MDgzNDgxJm1lc3NhZ2VpZD1NREItUFJELUJVTC0yMDE1MDQxNC40NDA4MzQ4MSZkYXRhYmFzZWlkPTEwMDEmc2VyaWFsPTE3NDM4MzU1JmVtYWlsaWQ9bWxlcHBlcnRAaGNwcm8uY29tJnVzZXJpZD1tbGVwcGVydEBoY3Byby5jb20mZmw9JmV4dHJhPU11bHRpdmFyaWF0ZUlkPSYmJg==&amp;&amp;&amp;102&amp;&amp;&amp;https://www.thunderclap.it/projects/24723-on-the-road-to-icd-10?locale=en\">Thunderclap</a> on the CMS website and sign in with your Facebook, Twitter, or Tumblr account.\r\n\r\nA message will be automatically released from participants’ selected accounts at 9 a.m. (Eastern) Thursday. The result will be a “thunderclap” of simultaneous Twitter, Facebook, and Tumblr posts about ICD-10 that will reverberate across social media.',
